{"tid":714993,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"到長崎尋找孫中山足跡之旅","createTime":"2018-06-24T06:02:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T07:49:39.000Z","uid":139685,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"88e363c8f5bf7a413723b8c4ace64e1d7e28d495","tid":714993,"uid":139685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T06:02:13.000Z","msg":"同樣是居住在海濱城市長崎，鈴木天眼與的梅屋莊吉舊宅相距很近，而鈴木之所以為人所銘記，乃是因為其所創辦的《東洋日出新聞》對辛亥革命予以了大量宣傳報導，孫中山因此而親自上門致謝並為報社題寫匾額。1913年3月，孫中山以全國鐵路督辦身份到訪長崎，專程趕來向抱恙在家的鈴木及其創辦的《東洋日出新聞》致謝，併合影留念。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《東洋日出新聞》的舊址位於油屋町，如今成為一座名為鶴茶庵的西餐館。在這座樓門口立有「孫文先生故緣之地」幾個字的小石碑。「在我看來，孫中山就像中國的坂本龍馬。」西餐館老闆川村這樣說。餐館裡面的牆上，掛有孫中山、鈴木天眼及宋慶齡等人的照片及資料，與早先掛上的龍馬像共同構成餐館一道獨特的風景線。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/140150_bd7253801abcbd77377b0fac8ceee88b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F140150_bd7253801abcbd77377b0fac8ceee88b.png&h=e6f3a8f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/140152_a30273fbbd65621f3f9a4d5505344fc4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F140152_a30273fbbd65621f3f9a4d5505344fc4.png&h=65acffdb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/140155_daa0ff84f646649270614a3bf6fb1aaf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F140155_daa0ff84f646649270614a3bf6fb1aaf.png&h=ac7ec8c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/140158_b2163c1fed6956ee0bd990603587427c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F140158_b2163c1fed6956ee0bd990603587427c.png&h=285acdad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff097b4f5dcca79aee7e0c03571904e6f98c2d4c","tid":714993,"uid":54359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T07:49:39.000Z","msg":"可以約佢食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一陣要出軍艦島 有咩需要注意意？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/714751/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/714751/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}